<title>NORWAY: Nycomed shares surge on merger deal.</title>
<headline>Nycomed shares surge on merger deal.</headline>
<dateline>OSLO 1997-07-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares in Norwegian pharmaceuticals company Nycomed ASA surged more than 24 percent early on Tuesday after a merger with Britain's Amersham International Plc was announced.</p>
